description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Nine Lives for East, Nine Lives for South, and 2 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80631-69924-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [63 Votes, Common]
